msgid "Create a Haystack Index"
msgstr ""

#: ../source/tutorial/build-a-geohaystack-index.txt:15
msgid ""
"A haystack index must reference two fields: the location field and a "
"second field. The second field is used for exact matches. Haystack "
"indexes return documents based on location and an exact match on a single"
" additional criterion. These indexes are not necessarily suited to "
"returning the closest documents to a particular location."
msgstr ""

#: ../source/tutorial/build-a-geohaystack-index.txt:21
